script.name: tv.lu.cmd.freighter
script.description: Cmd: Moves wares between one station and another

line.comment: * We don't want to make a run for energy every single time someone moves, so..
* If the source station is a dockwaremanaged station, we go by that.
* If it's not dock managed, just go by main capacity
* If the source doesn't have enough, detailed in our capacity settings, move on
* Current freighters are bringing back enough to top up
* Our test of station capacity, asuming all freighters heading there had loaded
* If we've made it this far, we have our source and ware
